9
0:0:48,36 --> 0:0:54,4
So if you could hunt it up for me,
I'll wait here.


10
0:0:54,4 --> 0:0:58,92
What kind of coffee do you do?


11
0:0:58,92 --> 0:1:1,36
This is a book shop, we don't do coffee.


12
0:1:1,36 --> 0:1:3,68
- The other book shops do.
- Listen, you...


13
0:1:3,68 --> 0:1:12,64
(Drowned out by grinding)


14
0:1:12,64 --> 0:1:16,12
This Schubert, this book search,
how does it work?


15
0:1:16,12 --> 0:1:21,76
Well, you know.
You just... and it pops up.


16
0:1:21,76 --> 0:1:25,4
We've a different sort of...


17
0:1:25,4 --> 0:1:27,8
here.


18
0:1:27,8 --> 0:1:29,52
Get on your knees.


19
0:1:29,52 --> 0:1:31,56
Put your hands on the floor.


20
0:1:31,56 --> 0:1:36,2
From where you are now
to that far corner is our music section.


21
0:1:36,2 --> 0:1:40,44
It's a bit mixed up with aviation,
botany and pregnancy.


22
0:1:40,44 --> 0:1:46,2
- Search!
- (Thunderous grinding)


23
0:1:46,2 --> 0:1:50,16
That is the kind of thing
that is going to put customers off.


24
0:1:50,16 --> 0:1:58,0
- (Grinding resumes)
- Go and see when the noise will stop!


25
0:1:58,0 --> 0:2:0,84
- (Grinding stops)
- Well?


26
0:2:0,84 --> 0:2:4,84
- (Grinding)
- (Drowned out)


27
0:2:4,84 --> 0:2:6,8
- (Grinding stops)
- What?


28
