(Drowned out by grinding)


29
0:2:10,12 --> 0:2:12,16
Just wait!


30
0:2:12,16 --> 0:2:15,96
(Grinding stops)


31
0:2:15,96 --> 0:2:19,28
(Grinding resumes)


32
0:2:19,28 --> 0:2:21,32
So what did he say?


33
0:2:21,32 --> 0:2:24,76
He'll start again after lunch,
it'll get worse tomorrow.


34
0:2:24,76 --> 0:2:29,4
- They wake you?
- Seven o'clock. I was doing my t'ai chi.


35
0:2:29,4 --> 0:2:32,56
It's not actually illegal to kill a builder.


36
0:2:32,56 --> 0:2:35,8
Hey, hey, hey! It's Sunday, right?


37
0:2:35,8 --> 0:2:37,12
- Yes.
- And we want to get away?


38
0:2:37,12 --> 0:2:39,36
- Yes.
- Why don't we...


39
0:2:39,36 --> 0:2:42,28
